## Key Conventions

- Use `@/` path aliases for imports (e.g., `@/components/ui/Button`)
- Use `cn()` utility for merging Tailwind classes
- Follow component patterns in `code-templates/frontend/`
- Follow design tokens in `ui/DESIGN_TOKENS.md`

## Commands

```bash
# Frontend Development
npm run dev          # Start frontend dev server at http://localhost:5173

# Backend Development
npm run dev:backend  # Start backend dev server at http://localhost:3000

# Build
npm run build        # TypeScript check + Vite build

# Preview
npm run preview      # Preview production build

# Lint
npm run lint         # ESLint check
```
